{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"vqbisdumti23oeq2xk6oml5","title":"String","desc":"","updated":1713902828857,"created":1711643845722,"custom":{},"fname":"lang.java.lib.string","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"cs"},"contentHash":"8a2ac75d9a77bdccfe3ff16fafea3680","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"lang.java.lib.string","id":"vqbisdumti23oeq2xk6oml5","vaultName":"cs"},"value":"dev.program.components.literal","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":32,"offset":32},"end":{"line":2,"column":66,"offset":66},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"dev.program.components.literal"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"lang.java.lib.string","id":"vqbisdumti23oeq2xk6oml5","vaultName":"cs"},"value":"arch.design.oo.patterns.immutable class","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":24,"offset":168},"end":{"line":3,"column":67,"offset":211},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"arch.design.oo.patterns.immutable class"}},{"from":{"fname":"lang.java.lib.string.buffer","id":"5kpsp95zn6nrn1y0k68w02w","vaultName":"cs"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":11,"offset":12},"end":{"line":3,"column":35,"offset":36},"indent":[]},"value":"lang.java.lib.string"},{"from":{"fname":"lang.java.lib.string.builder","id":"wrii2qem89nle2t4xy32nsv","vaultName":"cs"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":11,"offset":13},"end":{"line":4,"column":35,"offset":37},"indent":[]},"value":"lang.java.lib.string"},{"from":{"fname":"lang.java.jre.memory.lifecycle.methods.arguments","id":"9fx2k1xmp6jbhq9dr8oheij","vaultName":"cs"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":46,"offset":886},"end":{"line":14,"column":70,"offset":910},"indent":[]},"value":"lang.java.lib.string"}],"anchors":{"null-vs-empty-string":{"type":"header","text":"null vs empty String","value":"null-vs-empty-string","line":15,"column":0,"depth":1}},"children":["5kpsp95zn6nrn1y0k68w02w","wrii2qem89nle2t4xy32nsv","lltawdg3ubxo5lujxld7kff"],"parent":"9zir47v5yk3jbddsjyqkt53","data":{},"schema":{"schemaId":"string","moduleId":"lang"}},"body":"<h1 id=\"string\">String<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#string\"></a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>String literal</strong>: A string <a href=\"/cs/notes/8nki2c37f0299758ree1kij\">Literal</a> in Java is basically a sequence of characters from the source character set. </li>\n<li>String in Java is an <a href=\"/cs/notes/c5elrg6xfbs9jqfrh4kqo2e\">Immutable Class</a></li>\n<li>String literals initialised are an object of this String class.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>💡 While printing an object, Java compiler implicitly calls toString() method.</p>\n<h1 id=\"null-vs-empty-string\">null vs empty String<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#null-vs-empty-string\"></a></h1>\n<pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> getSome<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> getMose <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Both of them are not the same. <code>\"\"</code> is a literal and has a reference pointing to it in the String constant pool, while <code>getSome</code> has no value/reference in it so its null → default value for String.</p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/5kpsp95zn6nrn1y0k68w02w\">String Buffer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/wrii2qem89nle2t4xy32nsv\">String Builder</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/lltawdg3ubxo5lujxld7kff\">String Comparison</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/5kpsp95zn6nrn1y0k68w02w\">String Buffer (cs)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/wrii2qem89nle2t4xy32nsv\">String Builder (cs)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/9fx2k1xmp6jbhq9dr8oheij\">Passing Arguments (cs)</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id"